:false}},"faq_hAY6KU":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"question_ULzE7R":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"What Makes Titan Battlegear <em>The Safest?<\/em>","text":"<p>Titan Battlegear's hockey neck guard utilizes advanced American-made cut-resistant materials and a unique collar design to maximize coverage of critical zones.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"full_text","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_9NzEqE":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Other Brands Use Kevlar®, Why is Titan’s Titanotex™ Cut Resistance is Better?","text":"<p>Most <strong>Kevlar® fabrics offer an ANSI cut resistance level A2<\/strong>, and in very rare occasions level A3 (on a scale of A1 to A9).<\/p><p><strong>Titan's hockey neck guard shirt utilizes proprietary, American made fabrics, delivering the highest cut-resistance: level A9<\/strong>, which makes it 200 stronger than steel, and almost 5 times more cut resistant than Kevlar® products.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_QRwr6L":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Are there certifications for the USA Hockey mandated laceration protection?","text":"<p>New USA Hockey rules state that for a neck guard to qualify for all players 18 and under in the United States, they must have an HECC certification. <\/p><p>Currently the only brand available at major retailers with an HECC Certification is Titan BattleGear.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_hpTfXU":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"How Safe Is The Shirt After Many Washes?","text":"<p>We tested cleaning with cycles across TEN Durawash twin-tub industrial machines. This is equivalent to 50 washes in a domestic washing machine.<\/p><p><strong>The cut resistance level, following this washing process increased by 4%.<\/strong> Test reports from INTERTEK are available upon request.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_qX7VfM":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Where Are Titan's Products Produced?","text":"<p><strong>The United States of America!<\/strong> Titan was born in Florida and produced in St. Paul, MN, and has additional factories in North Carolina, New Jersey, and New York.<\/p><p><strong>The mass market and other independent brands produce in China<\/strong>, with questionable labor practices and superficial cut resistance certifications.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_74THLA":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Can I Customize Titan's Hockey Neck Guard Shirt With My Team Logo\/Colors?","text":"<p><strong>Yes<\/strong>, Titan's <a href=\"\/pages\/teamworks2\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Teamworks\">TeamWorks<\/a> program offers custom gear for teams, as well as personalization by player, including name, number, and even their country flag to represent their nationality!<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["question_ULzE7R","question_9NzEqE","question_QRwr6L","question_hpTfXU","question_qX7VfM","question_74THLA"],"settings":{"style":"with-background","heading":"FAQs","heading_size":"title-lg tracking-heading","heading_alignment":"text-left md:items-end md:flex-row","heading_tag":"h2","subheading":"","description":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","highlighted_reveal":false,"color_text":"#ffffff","color_background":"#000000","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"#000000","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"#000000","color_button_background":"#ffffff","color_button_gradient":"linear-gradient(54deg, rgba(114, 255, 179, 1) 14%, rgba(255, 250, 99, 1) 85%)","color_overlay":"#ffffff","overlay_opacity":4,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"divider":false,"narrow":false,"rounded":false}},"recently-viewed":{"type":"recently-viewed","custom_css":[".product-card__bottom.flex.items-center.gap-2 {display: none 